  <summary date="2017-03-01T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Respect for Peace Corps Volunteers Act 

 This bill amends the Peace Corps Act to allow the official seal or emblem and the name "Peace Corps" to be used on any death announcement, plaque, grave stone, or other grave marker of a former volunteer, officer, or employee of the Peace Corps.</summary>
